ygData.messageBody:
Forget playing in Cazic Thule if you are on the Fennin Ro server tho.
NOTHING and I mean Nothing! is spawning there. I was able to run around deep
within that dungeon, in full view, and not worry about getting jumped. There
just were no lizards anywhere....so my group left to go kill Sand Giants
instead <grin>

Lanadina
